  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dad\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The crisis in this country is getting worse",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The latest report of the World Food Program indicated that Sri Lanka's economic crisis is getting worse and according to the National Consumer Price Index, inflation increased from 58.9 percent in June to 66.7 percent in July.",
        "According to the report, the food security of Sri Lankans may be further affected due to rising inflation and rising prices of essential commodities.",
        "According to the report, 6.3 million Sri Lankans are already suffering from food insecurity. The latest report of the World Food Program indicated that the number of people suffering from food insecurity could increase further if there is no quick intervention in this problem.",
        "The World Food Program announced that it will continue to conduct telephone surveys on food security, nutrition, livelihood and credit of families covering all nine provinces of Sri Lanka.",
        "The World Food Program indicated that 34 percent of the 63 million US dollars needed to support Sri Lankans from July to December has been received as donations and another 42 million US dollars is needed."
      ],
